                <h2>What is Pipes?</h2>
    <p>Pipes is a free online service that lets you remix popular feed types and create data mashups using a visual editor. You can use Pipes to run your own web projects, or publish and share your own web services without ever having to write a line of code.  <a href="/web/docs?doc=overview">Learn more...</a></p>

